{"tid":1570156,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台或再失邦交國  海地勢危","createTime":"2019-09-15T02:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T04:34:49.000Z","uid":46356,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0fed914d09939e268cccaf1770de35cdfb20cab0","tid":1570156,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:39:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190915/20768493\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190915%2F20768493&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mDeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=dc905ca8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190915%2F20768493&h=d59d6570\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190915/20768493</a><br />\n陸再撬邦交國 海地勢危<br />\n<br />\n台灣面對斷交潮，或衝擊蔡英文的選情，近日盛傳太平洋島國所羅門群島將與台灣斷交，最快下周有決定。台灣當局在最後時刻力挽狂瀾，派外交官員出訪所羅門「箍煲」，爭取與所國總理會面，全力鞏固邦交。而除了所羅門，遠在中美洲的另一邦交國海地，亦被北京的「金錢攻勢」盯上。<br />\n<br />\n台派人赴所羅門「箍煲」<br />\n<br />\n據報道，大陸駐海地貿易發展事務處常駐代表王向陽（Wang Xiangyang）月初接受海地《新聞人報》專訪時表示，只要海地政府願維護「一個中國」原則，北京將願意與海地建立正式邦交，同時加強與海地在政治、經濟等方面的合作。王說：「中國現在國際事務上扮演的角色越來越重要&hellip;&hellip;除了免費援助外，（還可以）提供無息貸款及優惠貸款。」<br />\n<br />\n他又稱，中國將依照該國的需求，將經費投注在基礎建設等有龐大經費需求的地方。此外，王還會見了多名海地高級官員。台外交部昨澄清，台灣與海地邦交穩固，各項合作順利推動，並無斷交疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n至於所羅門亦正考慮是否與台斷交，台媒日前引述所國的跨黨派小組報告指，所羅門政府計劃9月中終止與台邦交，改與大陸建交。知情人士昨透露，外交部政務次長徐斯儉將在周末出行，預計周一抵達，全力鞏固邦交。另外，消息指美國將安排副總統彭斯，在9月17日的聯合國大會期間游說所國總理索格瓦雷，表達美國強烈支持台灣與所羅門維持良好關係的立場。<br />\n<br />\n所羅門是台灣在太平洋的六個邦交國之一，在1983年與台建交。自總統蔡英文上任後，台灣在大陸的打壓下已流失5個邦交國，只剩下17個，被形容是「雪崩式斷交」。<br />\n中央社"},{"pid":"0a3977cad776c582af2af1105e20dff60b14e3b8","tid":1570156,"uid":35790,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:43:27.000Z","msg":"做第2個波多黎各算啦"},{"pid":"2413277acd0524c008514178a1652f33a1f7d531","tid":1570156,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:45:36.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c8e575b71331ab5341f208a0d16360f435d2830","tid":1570156,"uid":85425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:47:37.000Z","msg":"奧巴緊真係養大左中共"},{"pid":"3ad32f278a6eea8daec43cf06c547659b8e2317d","tid":1570156,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T03:10:24.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n第五期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1569904/page/1</a><br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mDeipyOQHODmSSmjwmLFmyk%3D&h=f51337de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"a752a5362fc37fcd8a0f083345ca35e361ed0bb3","tid":1570156,"uid":146720,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0fed914d09939e268cccaf1770de35cdfb20cab0","tid":1570156,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T02:39:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20190915/20768493\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%